{"tid":2434693,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"班培生培心係咪完全諗唔到鍾共有咩優點","createTime":"2021-03-05T16:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T09:08:01.000Z","uid":132322,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3240e55c6cb3bd9d872b490e8420cc025566ce","tid":2434693,"uid":132322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"成日淨係識一句：有錢大晒，你聽日咪又係要返工幫鍾(狗)生返工<br />\n有錢係有特權，但係有特權唔代表你個人唔垃圾唔廢呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇見過人叫李嘉誠做誠狗？人地有錢又識做生意，又識教仔守本，似足你咁淨係識敗身家咩？<br />\n仲有，有冇發現你同你班狗嘅口吻似足中国啲無品無格嘅暴發戶？有錢係隻手遮天，但係你遮唔到人地嘅評價呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好扮自己有錢所以唔緊其他人講咩，你呢幾個月搞咁多嘢咪就係想攞認同感，想人拜你，想人讚你而唔係話你淨係識敗家<br />\n結果咪露返晒底，仲衰到同大陸佬同lv，唔怪得知話醫護係雞啦"},{"pid":"96d15957233a953c93c6051d70c6c297c3267715","tid":2434693,"uid":60434,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"賠生成世人都係咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打機淨係識掉錢，掉完錢都係比人撚到輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46144a1a32262a9d266a974213728f162fec92df","tid":2434693,"uid":132322,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"96d15957233a953c93c6051d70c6c297c3267715","tid":2434693,"uid":60434,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"賠生成世人都係咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打機淨係識掉錢，掉完錢都係比人撚到輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"傻閪嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要柒到連個柒碌toyz都搞唔掂<br />\n依家照樣搵到飯食有廣告接<br />\n好意思覺得自己好撚威威"},{"pid":"fab4e1a75e5ae18b40024596b424deaf4066396c","tid":2434693,"uid":10520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2